JOHANNESBURG, South Africa, June 14, 2018/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            Pan-African broadcast network Kwese TV (Kwese.ESPN.com) is bringing the Rugby Africa Gold Cup 2018 live and exclusive on Kwesé Free Sports, Kwesé Sports 1, the newly launched Kwesé Iflix and Facebook Live from 16 June to 18 August. As the exclusive rights-holder for both TV and all digital platforms, Kwesé TV will be using local facility houses to deliver excellent and seamless coverage of the tournament.
        
                
            
                
                                
                
                
